{"tid":1468532,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"對外媒來講 阻機有咩新聞價值呀","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:59.000Z","uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c30017197aeb675e0eda3c28c941e834e0bc9e29","tid":1468532,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:09.000Z","msg":"用下腦喇唔該"},{"pid":"a0552c75eb8e79ad0d149639a65858e4f1e48e81","tid":1468532,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔會割蓆，但我地亦都會持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩建議大家投票解決，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所以社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，可貴之處就係識得自省，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要認，認完就要反省，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏<br />\n<br />\n如果出現失誤唔去承認，唔去反省，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。"},{"pid":"daced12eccf6ba199aead23b643310d9daa5a5bd","tid":1468532,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=